  "stem": "<p>Which expression is equivalent to <math><mn>6</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>6</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>5</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></math> ?</p>",
