  "rationale": "<p>The greatest common factor of 6x⁶, 10x⁵, and 8x⁴ is 2x⁴ (smallest power of x is 4; gcd(6,10,8) = 2). Factoring gives 2x⁴(3x² − 5x + 4). Choice (a) is correct.</p>",
